snippet.title: The War Within Features Overview | World of Warcraft
snippet.description:
From deep beneath the surface comes visions of the Harbinger of the Void. Hear the call and dive into the opening chapter of The Worldsoul Saga story arc with the newest expansion World of Warcraft: The War Within: coming in 2024. 

Pre-purchase the Epic Edition of World of Warcraft: The War Within and unlock rewards today: https://shop.battle.net/product/world-of-warcraft-the-war-within?utm_source=youtube.com&utm_campaign=mktg-wow-global-11-prepurchase&utm_medium=video&utm_content=yt_video
Learn more and pre-purchase today at https://worldofwarcraft.com/

► Latest WoW news: http://worldofwarcraft.com/news
